itas em clientes. Do design ao alojamento, tratamos de tudo.</p><a class=\"group mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-pill bg-white text-black text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 transition-all hover:bg-white/90\" href=\"/servicos/web\">Saber mais<span class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"relative h-[240px] md:h-[340px] w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[radial-gradient(120%_120%_at_70%_0%,rgb(var(--accent-rgb)_/_0.10),transparent_55%)] bg-[#0c0d10] overflow-hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#101216] shadow-[0_24px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2.5 border-b border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03]\"><span class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f57]/80\"></span><span class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#febc2e]/80\"></span><span class=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]/80\"></span><div class=\"ml-2 flex-1 h-5 rounded-full bg-white/[0.06] flex items-center px-2.5 text-[10px] text-dark\">apiariosterrasdapulga.pt</div></div><div class=\"relative w-full aspect-[16/10]\"><img alt=\"Website Apiários Terras da Pulga, criado pela Element Group\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-top\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 90vw, 360px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2FProjetos%2Fapiariospulga.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-5 right-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-bg-card/90 backdrop-blur p-3 shadow-[0_16px_36px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]\"><p class=\"text-[10px] text-muted\">PageSpeed</p><div class=\"flex items-end gap-1.5\"><span class=\"text-2xl font-heading font-medium text-white leading-none\">98</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-accent mb-0.5\">/ 100</span></div></div></div></div></article></div><div class=\"sticky pb-8\" style=\"top:126px\"><article style=\"--accent-rgb:111 179 154;--accent:#6FB39A;--accent-deep:#2f6b58;--accent-mid:#4f8f7a;--accent-light:#bfe6d8\" class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a1d24] via-[#131417] to-[#0F0F0E] shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)]\"><div class=\"absolute -top-16 -left-16 w-80 h-80 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16), rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0) 60%)\"></div><div class=\"relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center p-8 md:p-12\"><div class=\"max-w-md\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent/90 mb-4\">Categoria 02 · Visibilidade &amp; SEO</p><h3 class=\"text-white\">SEO e Otimização para apareceres no Google</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Colocamos o teu negócio à frente de quem procura: SEO técnico, SEO local (Top 3 no Google Maps) e conteúdo otimizado para as pesquisas certas. Em média, os nossos projetos de SEO geram 3,2× mais tráfego orgânico.</p><a class=\"group mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-pill bg-white text-black text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 transition-all hover:bg-white/90\" href=\"/servicos/seo\">Saber mais<span class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"relative h-[240px] md:h-[340px] w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[radial-gradient(120%_120%_at_70%_0%,rgb(var(--accent-rgb)_/_0.10),transparent_55%)] bg-[#0c0d10] overflow-hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 p-5 md:p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2.5\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-[340px] rounded-xl bg-white shadow-[0_20px_44px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3.5\"><span class=\"font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-none tracking-tight select-none\"><span style=\"color:#4285F4\">G</span><span style=\"color:#EA4335\">o</span><span style=\"color:#FBBC05\">o</span><span style=\"color:#4285F4\">g</span><span style=\"color:#34A853\">l</span><span style=\"color:#EA4335\">e</span></span><div class=\"flex-1 flex items-center gap-2 h-7 rounded-full border border-[#dfe1e5] px-3\"><span class=\"text-[11.5px] text-[#3c4043] truncate\">massagens são romão</span><svg class=\"ml-auto shrink-0\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"#4285F4\" stroke-width=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"m20 20-3-3\" stroke=\"#4285F4\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-1\"><span class=\"grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] text-white text-[9px] font-semibold shrink-0\">M</span><span class=\"leading-tight min-w-0\"><span class=\"block text-[11px] text-[#202124] truncate\">Maria Mendes Massagens</span><span class=\"block text-[10px] text-[#5f6368] truncate\">mariamendesmassagens.pt</span></span></div><p class=\"text-[15px] leading-snug text-[#1a0dab] line-clamp-2\">Maria Mendes — Massagens de Relaxamento · São Romão</p><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-[11.5px] leading-snug text-[#4d5156] line-clamp-2\">Massagens de relaxamento em Seia. Reserve o seu momento de bem-estar — corporais, faciais, aromaterapia e mais.</p></div><div class=\"mt-3.5 opacity-70\"><div class=\"h-1.5 w-20 rounded bg-[#dadce0] mb-1.5\"></div><div class=\"h-2.5 w-3/5 rounded bg-[#aac0e8] mb-1.5\"></div><div class=\"h-1.5 w-full rounded bg-[#e8eaed]\"></div></div></div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-dark\">↑ Resultado real no Google</span></div></div></div></article></div><div class=\"sticky pb-8\" style=\"top:152px\"><article style=\"--accent-rgb:169 138 212;--accent:#A98AD4;--accent-deep:#543f7d;--accent-mid:#7d63ad;--accent-light:#ddccf0\" class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a1d24] via-[#131417] to-[#0F0F0E] shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)]\"><div class=\"absolute -top-16 -left-16 w-80 h-80 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16), rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0) 60%)\"></div><div class=\"relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center p-8 md:p-12\"><div class=\"max-w-md\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent/90 mb-4\">Categoria 03 · Social Media</p><h3 class=\"text-white\">Gestão de Redes Sociais e Campanhas que vendem</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Gerimos as tuas redes sociais com conteúdo e design profissional e campanhas pagas (Meta e Google Ads) que atraem os clientes certos — não só seguidores. Presença consistente, todos os dias, sem te tirar tempo.</p><a class=\"group mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-pill bg-white text-black text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 transition-all hover:bg-white/90\" href=\"/servicos/social\">Saber mais<span class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a></div><div class=\"relative h-[240px] md:h-[340px] w-full rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[radial-gradient(120%_120%_at_70%_0%,rgb(var(--accent-rgb)_/_0.10),transparent_55%)] bg-[#0c0d10] overflow-hidden\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolu