p=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-muted/80\">Contacto direto e próximo</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white/[0.04] text-white/30\" aria-label=\"Não\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6l12 12M18 6L6 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-muted/80\">Domina só uma área</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 grid place-items-center w-5 h-5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white/[0.04] text-white/30\" aria-label=\"Não\"><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6l12 12M18 6L6 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"text-muted/80\">Sem continuidade garantida</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-muted text-sm max-w-lg mx-auto\">O melhor dos dois mundos: <span class=\"text-white\">qualidade de agência</span> e<!-- --> <span class=\"text-white\">agilidade de freelancer</span> — sem o preço alto nem a espera.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/10\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-white\">O que dizem de trabalhar comigo</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto\">Para além do resultado, o que fica é a relação — próxima, honesta e sem dores de cabeça.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-8 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-start gap-5 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-8 shrink-0 w-full lg:w-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(40px)\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-[160px] h-[200px] md:w-[240px] md:h-[260px] rounded-2xl shrink-0 grid place-items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/80 to-[#2f4f7a] text-white font-heading font-semibold\" style=\"font-size:44px\">CE</span><div class=\"max-w-sm\"><h4 class=\"text-white\">Cliente Element Group</h4><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">“<!-- -->Desde o primeiro dia falei sempre com a mesma pessoa. Explicou tudo sem complicar e respondia em minutos — fez-me sentir que o meu negócio importava mesmo.<!-- -->”</p><p class=\"mt-6 text-white/80 text-sm\">Negócio local · Portugal</p></div></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-5 shrink-0\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-[130px] h-[260px] rounded-2xl shrink-0 opacity-90 grid place-items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/80 to-[#2f4f7a] text-white font-heading font-semibold\" style=\"font-size:44px\">CE</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-[130px] h-[260px] rounded-2xl shrink-0 opacity-90 grid place-items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/80 to-[#2f4f7a] text-white font-heading font-semibold\" style=\"font-size:44px\">CE</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-[130px] h-[260px] rounded-2xl shrink-0 opacity-90 grid place-items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/80 to-[#2f4f7a] text-white font-heading font-semibold\" style=\"font-size:44px\">CE</span></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><button class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/20 text-white flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white hover:text-bg transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Testemunho anterior\">←</button><button class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/20 text-white flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white hover:text-bg transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Testemunho seguinte\">→</button></div><span class=\"text-muted text-sm\">1<!-- -->/<!-- -->1</span></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/10\" aria-labelledby=\"faq\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Quanto custa um website?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Os nossos websites começam em 297€, com preço fixo definido à cabeça — sem custos escondidos. O valor final depende do que precisas (site institucional, loja online, número de páginas) e dizemos-te tudo na proposta gratuita, antes de avançares.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Quanto tempo demora a ter o meu site pronto?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Depende da dimensão do projeto: um site institucional fica normalmente pronto mais depressa do que uma loja online completa. Depois de conversarmos, indicamos um prazo concreto na proposta — e cumprimo-lo.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Preciso de perceber de tecnologia ou tratar do domínio e alojamento?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Não. Tratamos de tudo por ti — design, desenvolvimento, domínio e alojamento. Só precisas de nos dizer o que queres para o teu negócio; a parte técnica é connosco.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Já tenho um site. Conseguem melhorá-lo?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sim. Podemos redesenhar, acelerar (PageSpeed 95+) e otimizar para SEO o teu site atual, ou criar um novo de raiz — o que fizer mais sentido para os teus objetivos e orçamento.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Trabalham com o meu setor e com a minha zona?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Trabalhamos com PMEs de praticamente qualquer setor, em todo o Portugal — presencialmente ou à distância. Especializamo-nos em pequenos e médios negócios, não em grandes multinacionais.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"O que acontece depois do site estar online?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Não desaparecemos. Temos planos mensais de manutenção, SEO e gestão de redes para o teu negócio continuar a crescer — mas sem obrigação: o site é teu e continuas connosco só se quiseres.\"}}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start\"><div class=\"md:sticky md:top-28\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-white/10 bg-bg-card p-8 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_0%,rgba(127,168,217,0.16),rgba(14,14,14,0)_60%)]\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.10]\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:34px 34px\"></div><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1c2738] to-[#0f1318] border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(127,168,217,0.4)]\"><img alt=\"Element Group\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-9 h-9\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fweb-app-manifest-512x512.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fweb-app-manifest-512x512.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fweb-app-manifest-512x512.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"mt-7 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark\">FAQ</p><h2 id=\"faq\" class=\"mt-2 text-white\">Ainda com dúvidas?</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs\">Fala connosco sem compromisso. Respondemos em menos de 2 horas com tudo o que precisas de saber.</p><div class=\"mt-7\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"/contacto\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Pedir orçamento grátis</span></a></div><div class=\"mt-7 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-muted\"><span class=\"text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\">★</span>5,0 no Google · resposta em &lt; 2h</div></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n                    border-accent/30 bg-bg-card\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-0\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-0\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\"><span class=\"font-heading text-base md:text-lg transition-colors text-white\">Quanto custa um website?</span><span class=\"relative w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-4 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-current\"></span><span class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-0 w-0.5 h-4 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-current transition-transform duration-300 scale-y-0\"></span></span></button></h3><div id=\"faq-a-0\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"faq-q-0\" class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:auto;opacity:1\"><p class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">Os nossos websites começam em 297€, com preço fixo definido à cabeça — sem custos escondidos. O valor final depende do que precisas (site institucional, loja online, número de páginas) e dizemos-te tudo na proposta gratuita, antes de avançares.</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border transition-colors duration-300\n                    border-white/10 bg-bg-card/40 hover:border-white/20\"><h3><button id=\"faq-q-1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"faq-a-1\" class=\"w-full text-left px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent rounded-2xl\">